title="Jon Sterling">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Why can’t we define <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[F_{\mathcal {P}{\mathopen {}\left (M\right )\mathclose {}}}]]></fr:tex> to be the set of singletons <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathopen {}\left \{q\right \}\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[q\in F_{M}]]></fr:tex>?</fr:p><fr:tree
